CFC Stanbic Equity Desk to Be Headed by Ex-World Bank Official, Daily Says

-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 
2011-07-07T04:10:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/cfc-stanbic-equity-desk-to-be-headed-by-ex-world-bank-official-daily-says.html
CFC Stanbic Holdings Ltd. (CFCB)  hired
former World Bank official Marcel Mballa-Ekobena to head its
equity-research desk in Nairobi, the Kenyan capital, Business
Daily reported.  Mballa-Ekobena was previously portfolio officer at the
International Finance Corp., where he was in charge of private-
equity investments in  Latin America , the newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Paul Richardson  at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  